 "contentEncoded": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/sduck409/4582916696/in/pool-nashvillest\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4033/4582916696_c4c7fdcb52.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<ul>\n<li>Our damage tally is now up to a cool $1.56 billion, and that&#x2019;s just private homes and businesses. Sidewalks, roads, water systems and all that stuff will likely set us back quite a bit more. [<a href=\"http://nashvillecitypaper.com/content/2010-flood/damages-homes-businesses-156-billion-mayor-says?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed:+NashvilleCityPaper-LatestNews+(Nashville+City+Paper+-+Latest+News)&amp;utm_content=Google+Reader\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillecitypaper.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">City Paper</a>]</li>\n<li>Aw shucks, Chief Serpas. Why you leaving us so soon? Was it something we said? Was it something about the weather? [<a href=\"http://nashvillecitypaper.com/content/city-news/serpas-resignation-effective-today?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed:+NashvilleCityPaper-LatestNews+(Nashville+City+Paper+-+Latest+News)&amp;utm_content=Google+Reader\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillecitypaper.com&apos;]);\">City Paper</a>]</li>\n<li>Since we&#x2019;re definitely glass-half-full thinkers here at Nashvillest, we&#x2019;d like to think that the sudden influx of contractors hiring is actually a good thing. [<a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/money/23507310/detail.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WSMV</a>]</li>\n<li>The Tennessee Supreme Court is giving some folks an extra 30 days to file court papers if their original deadlines were between May 3rd and May 7th. [<a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/global/story.asp?s=12458607\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WTVF</a>]</li>\n<li>Sen. Lamar Alexander has jumped on the &#x201C;Tennessee is awesome because we don&#x2019;t loot&#x201D; bandwagon. [<a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20100510/NEWS01/100510053/-1/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Tennessean</a>]</li>\n<li>Titans season ticket holders now have until Friday to renew. [<a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20100510/SPORTS01/100510013/-1/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Tennessean</a>]</li>\n<li>You guys have been killing us with the <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#search?q=floodsongs\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;twitter.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_self\">#floodsongs</a> thing on Twitter all afternoon. Thanks for the laugh!</li>\n</ul>\n</p><p><em>Photo by </em><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/sduck409/4582916696/in/pool-nashvillest\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\"><em>sduck409</em></a><em>.</em></p>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Related posts:<ol><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2008/06/19/happy-hour-the-merits-of-proofreading/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Happy Hour: The Merits Of Proofreading\">Happy Hour: The Merits Of Proofreading</a></li>\n</ol></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"
